query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS events (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  app_id INT NOT NULL,
  event_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  event_type VARCHAR(50),
  user_id VARCHAR(100),
  device_id VARCHAR(100),
  properties JSON,
  created_at DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
